{"tid":1654401,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"城大：強烈譴責「不明人士」包圍本地生對話　重視非本地生意見","createTime":"2019-10-14T14:51:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T15:08:19.000Z","uid":15696,"like":8,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4396a03348f9ccf428446c9d4332c8a641d1d727","tid":1654401,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T14:51:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">原來本地生係「不明人士」 會都取撚消埋<br />\n內地生意見就照聽 果然係shity</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n緊急事故應變小組通告（三十二）<br />\n<br />\n經過各方交流，大學訂於今天舉行三場分別與本地生、非本地生與研究生等的對話。<br />\n<br />\n但是，非常令人意外，在首場與本地本科生對話開展前，<span style=\"color: red;\">會場被大批身份不明人士包圍，阻擋對話。情況混亂、危及安全，甚至影響工作人員的身體，需召喚救護車。</span>基於安全理由，校方<span style=\"color: red;\">取消對話</span>，並為以下行為深表譴責：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不明人士包圍會場，以粗言穢語叫囂辱罵工作、保安人員，危害安全，破壞公物。</span><br />\n<br />\n杯葛對話，對已登記的學生進場構成極大困難。<br />\n而原訂早上11時30分，在另一個場地進行的與非本地本科生對話，由於現場已經有約20名學生在會場完成登記入場，<span style=\"color: red;\">大學職員藉此機會與他們繼續交流，他們對現況及校園安全表示極度憂慮。</span><br />\n<br />\n大學一直透過不同渠道和方法與學生和教職員溝通，聆聽大家的需要及提供適切支援。對於今天的對話安排被迫取消，我們深表遺憾並表示憂慮。<br />\n<br />\n我們會把已經收集到<span style=\"color: red;\">逾100條的問題（非本地本科生？）</span>，整理之後，適時透過大學公告向全體學生及教職員公布。大學會繼續跟城大理性的師生對話，<span style=\"color: red;\">外界切勿干擾</span>。<br />\n<br />\n緊急事故應變小組主席<br />\n<br />\n副校長（學生事務）葉豪盛教授<br />\n副校長（行政）李惠光先生<br />\n2019年10月14日"},{"pid":"68b72c56757c589c154c83582505843b487b5d05","tid":1654401,"uid":15696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T14:52:32.000Z","msg":"城大人仲繼續上堂？　諗住就咁算？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af644389d334a053a3d6acb8a9bf1eb982596f04","tid":1654401,"uid":295218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T14:53:03.000Z","msg":"VTC同學速入)讓陳同學沉冤得雪！！！還其家人一個公道！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1654230\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1654230</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n可以嘅話，幫手推同share岀去，等聽日多啲人集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11f2ff55858a91f4e6bb4f946a72c3ba44366dc2","tid":1654401,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T14:54:25.000Z","msg":"城大人呢?"},{"pid":"ddd381368dc24865991fbe988d658bb561847479","tid":1654401,"uid":125380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T14:55:46.000Z","msg":"城大人 成大器去左邊"},{"pid":"43fca7cf64d584d559b43396a58eb1a2e059a7d0","tid":1654401,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T14:56:07.000Z","msg":"點解會比中大OU冷淡咁多?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca1630e49eac8736831ac463a9790dfdf5b3f61f","tid":1654401,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T14:56:51.000Z","msg":"人呢?"},{"pid":"50291442c2fa860150ebc90ce55bea9bb8e57ef9","tid":1654401,"uid":262146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T14:58:30.000Z","msg":"垃圾shitty"},{"pid":"c841d15180b98b95233da4b6ea1482421a0735d1","tid":1654401,"uid":15696,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T14:58:32.000Z","msg":"根本今日唔算勁多人都搞起咁<br />\nshitty 高層簡直係不可回收垃圾"},{"pid":"85b6da022b50b0bea4f9e39c7817e4c6e3fb76dc","tid":1654401,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T14:59:20.000Z","msg":"要控制一間大學，必先控制校長"},{"pid":"ae8e30710d19909b508831bca026637e25bd27ec","tid":1654401,"uid":194968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T14:59:29.000Z","msg":"郭位肯出黎面對未？"},{"pid":"73c0007796a44af28d3b5e4aedd5c5744ce36838","tid":1654401,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T14:59:36.000Z","msg":"人哋D副校起碼叫有人樣<br />\n呢2件係咩嚟"},{"pid":"fbe8f352492e98d402a9c7bc6fe901164acf4217","tid":1654401,"uid":100712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T15:00:15.000Z","msg":"城大人 始終 追唔上 暴大勇武"},{"pid":"60e62df657038e8558be159b43942e96c8dab505","tid":1654401,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T15:00:58.000Z","msg":"城大人去左邊   暴大傾到爆到POST<br />\n幾時再去抗議 ?"},{"pid":"8fb77f73edbd9bb7e206382d80b4c0400ad9f1e9","tid":1654401,"uid":215763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T15:01:05.000Z","msg":"讀左咁耐都冇見過郭位真人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\non9到個見面會得兩位副校長，郭位繼續深潛"},{"pid":"8afb86935e79d58a607f8c2c6c484c0f18fc034d","tid":1654401,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85b6da022b50b0bea4f9e39c7817e4c6e3fb76dc","tid":1654401,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T14:59:20.000Z","msg":"要控制一間大學，必先控制校長"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T15:01:42.000Z","msg":"禽賊先禽走狗"},{"pid":"5091da9c04023b66c0b18ee3da5163f72723bc28","tid":1654401,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T15:02:38.000Z","msg":"與梁振英關係爭論<br />\n<br />\n郭位曾被香港媒體報導形容為追隨梁振英的「梁粉」[27][28]。但資料顯示郭位並非由梁振英任命為校長，郭位於2008年5月由美國到香港上任時，梁振英仍為嶺南大學校董會主席；梁振英在2008年10月22日才正式出任城大校董會主席 <br />\n<br />\n兩岸關係與政治立場<br />\n郭位曾頒贈中國國民黨前主席連戰榮譽博士，除連戰之外，城市大學曾頒贈榮譽博士予台灣各界人士，包括林百里、李開復、鄭崇華及翁啟惠等。<br />\n<br />\n郭位曾在2013年7月19日邀郝柏村演講「武力統一與和平統一：中國式民主的特色是什麼？」。<br />\n<br />\n郭位在香港學界於2014年9月發起大罷課時被城大學生要求表態[31]。2014年城大學生罷課期間，郭位親自接收學生請願信，其後再與學生代表會面，承諾為學生提供各種適當支援。香港佔領中環運動發生之初，郭位於10月5日晚縮短外訪由美國回港，立即趕赴金鐘現場探望城大學生，關心慰問學生人身安全。<br />\n<br />\n為推動台港文化交流， 郭位曾促使城市大學與國立故宮博物院合作，於2015年主辦 同安．潮－新媒體藝術展。 <br />\n<br />\n2015年9月，郭位以香港城市大學校長身份受邀，與近500位來自香港不同界別的人士，包括其他6位香港政府資助大學校長 (4位受政府邀請、2位以港區政協身份出席)前往北京參觀閱兵。"},{"pid":"bf32260ac8d6c7aa65090e70a1c17a27b0aa6ae8","tid":1654401,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T15:04:03.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】城大兩名副校長今日會與學生舉行閉門會談，一批城大學生遊行至會談場地，要求與校長郭位公開對話。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">二十多個城大學生穿上黑衫和戴口罩</span>，在城大王氏國際廣場集合。他們手持橫額，遊行至閉門會談的場地劉鳴煒學術樓，促請校方譴責警暴。<br />\n<br />\n部分人原本獲邀出席會談，但他們表明不會進場，杯葛對話，批評校方安排每場會談只邀請40人，只有一小時會面，加上對話不公開，要求與校長郭位公開對話。<br />\n<br />\n城大今天安排了三場閉門會談，由兩名副校長出席，超過三百人報名。"},{"pid":"9576076a2b007631c4306788d9c0d1a21a64e91e","tid":1654401,"uid":128117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T15:04:35.000Z","msg":"留名等睇城大被裝修 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4df610ab17b91dbd2ce1c008e13220850683670f","tid":1654401,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T15:04:45.000Z","msg":"仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed1e110582d01920b5b2354a02b03eec325a3f09","tid":1654401,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T15:04:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">二十多個城大學生 = 不明人士<br />\n二十多個城大學生 = 校園安全極度憂慮<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"4f05b7d0301cc67ea766f7b0af728ff32a198d63","tid":1654401,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T15:05:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z0ZKS4J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ0ZKS4J.jpg&h=1d7d1687&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n今日得咁少人"},{"pid":"4c4ec62ed9b748768ba0f6cbaeb1d661e21fcd1a","tid":1654401,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f05b7d0301cc67ea766f7b0af728ff32a198d63","tid":1654401,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T15:05:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z0ZKS4J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ0ZKS4J.jpg&h=1d7d1687&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n今日得咁少人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T15:06:29.000Z","msg":"要人要咗咁耐<br />\nD人去撚咗邊?"},{"pid":"ed018dc95367bb1b8e2866c8a0ed6db33649a200","tid":1654401,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c4ec62ed9b748768ba0f6cbaeb1d661e21fcd1a","tid":1654401,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f05b7d0301cc67ea766f7b0af728ff32a198d63","tid":1654401,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T15:05:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z0ZKS4J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ0ZKS4J.jpg&h=1d7d1687&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n今日得咁少人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T15:06:29.000Z","msg":"要人要咗咁耐<br />\nD人去撚咗邊?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T15:07:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">城大人出嚟面對</span>"},{"pid":"542e436c8cb561090f822b7c5a91e36dc5db4db4","tid":1654401,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T15:08:19.000Z","msg":"城大人呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}